                        <interp inst="t18400914-name-234" type="given" value="LOUSIA"></interp>LOUSIA PEARSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I was left at home, and the time-piece was there—the prisoner came back, and asked me if my mother had taken the time-piece—I said she had not—he asked if I could take it—I sent my little sister with it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400914-name-235" type="witnessName">
