                        <interp inst="t18400914-name-235" type="given" value="MARY ANN"></interp>MARY ANN PEARSON</persName>
                  </hi>. My sister sent me with the time-piece—the prisoner took me as far as the haircutter's, and told me to go back and fetch a wrapper—he had the time-piece—I went back, and saw no more of it—I am sure the prisoner is the man.</p>
